org.perfcake.message.receiver

Class AbstractReceiver

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.perfcake.message.receiver.AbstractReceiver
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Receiver
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractAutoSpawnReceiver, HttpReceiver

    public abstract class AbstractReceiver
extends Object
implements Receiver
    Default implementation of basic receiver methods. We do not want them as default implementations in the interface because we want protected visibility of the fields.
    Author:
    Martin Večeřa
